item.description: Join us at PWF 2011, a fun(d)-raising event to benefit continuing education and support for current and potential visiting teams at New England Pet Partners, Inc, a non-profit 501(c)(3), enhancing well-being and education with pet-assisted therapy and Reading with Dogs. Pets get massaged, TTouched and Reiki'd. Meet the therapy dog teams, wellness contributors and authors. Enjoy the human stuff too, while having fun at a worthwhile cause! Non-competitive agilty will be outdoors weather permitting. Connect, network, breathe and enjoy! Learn more at http://www.petwellnes...
